      "explanation": {
        "concept": "Combination of 'some', 'all', and 'no' relationships allows deduction via chaining and exclusion.",
        "step_by_step": [
          "Some cars ∩ bikes",
          "All bikes ⊆ trucks",
          "No trucks ∩ planes",
          "So cars connected to bikes are also connected to trucks, hence not planes",
          "Thus all three conclusions are valid"
